{
  "texts": [
    "In comparison to anticipated human performance levels, the best model configurations (GPT-4+CoT+SC+Thresholding and GPT-4+CoT+SC) position between the top 10% and 20% of human performance.",
    "This study underscores that although LLMs demonstrate robust performance across various tasks, they are prone to errors when faced with complex tasks.",
    "SciEval (Sun et al., 2023) is another benchmark for natural sciences domain.",
    "It includes 18,000 scientific questions in three disciplines: chemistry, physics, and biology.",
    "The questions consist of three parts: the question, multiple-choice answers and the correct answer."
  ]
}